ourers online registration form.", "002-normal": "To read the complete Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana details, click at the link \u2013 [Haryana Labour Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana](https://hrylabour.gov.in/bocw/settings/schemeDetail/116)."}, "004-section": {"000-title": "Haryana Labour Welfare Board Assistance for Medical Treatment Scheme Eligibility", "001-normal": "Under the \u091a\u093f\u0915\u093f\u0924\u094d\u0938\u093e \u0938\u0939\u093e\u092f\u0924\u093e \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e of Haryana Labour Welfare Board, labour dept. provide minimum wages to the laborers admitted in hospitals suffering from accident / major disease. These wages would be given when the laborer got admitted in govt. / govt. aided hospitals for 4 to 30 days duration. The rates of wages would be same as those fixed as minimum wages by the Haryana government under Haryana Labour Assistance for Medical Treatment Scheme. To avail the assistance, candidates must fulfill the eligibility criteria as shown below:-", "002-table": {"row": 5, "column": 1, "data": [["Eligibility / \u092a\u093e\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0924\u093e"], ["Membership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u0937", "1"], ["Apply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093e", "1"], ["Scheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f", "All"], ["Continue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940", "No"]]}}, "005-section": {"000-title": "Haryana Labour Department Chikitsa Sahayata Yojana Conditions", "001-listElement": "- All the registered labourers must have minimum 1 years of membership / subscription.", "002-listElement": "- In the identity certificate of the registered labourers, date of application and subscription amount needs to be mentioned.", "003-listElement": "- All the laborers must be admitted for treatment in govt. / govt. aided hospitals for minimum 4 